Certificate generation process
==============================
CA(Certificate,private key)
Private key is required to sign the CSR.
Public key is available to clients

Cert Gen Client
================
CSR(indentity info,public key)
CSR is submitted to CA and CA performs validation and issue certificate.

The CA should be trusted by the cliients who will verify the certificate issued by the server.



